{"data": {"__GLOBAL": {"_ATTACH_BASE_VIEW": "img.nga.178.com/attachments"}, "__U": {"150058": {"uid": 150058, "username": "UID:150058", "credit": 135537154, "medal": "272,207,157,92", "reputation": "28_30,61_0,147_775,130_10", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 73, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1123989606, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 41079, "rvrc": 29, "money": 90765, "thisvisit": 1782044211, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135537154}, "66989363": {"uid": 66989363, "username": "UID:66989363", "credit": 135275008, "medal": null, "reputation": "147_-300", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 39, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1762774156, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 2701, "rvrc": 10, "money": 0, "thisvisit": 1782082361, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135275008}, "__GROUPS": {"73": ["学徒", 360672, 73], "39": ["学徒", 98528, 39]}, "__MEDALS": {"272": ["272.gif", "棒棒糖", "叔叔请你吃棒棒糖", 272], "207": ["207.gif", "爆竹声中旧岁除", "一支红杏出墙来", 207], "157": ["157.gif", "王者之剑", "王者之剑活动纪念", 157], "92": ["92.gif", "小心死亡之翼-", "2011年大灾变开服纪念", 92]}, "__REPUTATIONS": {"147": {"150058": 775, "66989363": -300, "0": "大时代"}}}, "__R": [{"pid": 864548038, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 7, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 14:53", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864547806,45974302,3769]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=4808320]munilaomu[/uid] (2026-04-14 14:51):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，但是胜宏和生益这些pcb大屁股还在拉啊[/quote]<br/>胜宏？？？不同世界线?", "lou": 2040, "content_length": 26, "reply_to": 864547806, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776149591}, {"pid": 864548280, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 38, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 14:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "一波狂暴拉升 散户又开始进场追了 结果发现和后半段涨的东西不一样[s:ac:哭笑]", "lou": 2041, "content_length": 58, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776149697}, {"pid": 864548488, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 106, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 14:56", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你看你们  涨起来懂追了  前面我说更新目标到4030-4035的时候为什么不买<br/><br/>噢  看不起我  <br/><br/>也是合理[s:ac:哭笑]", "lou": 2042, "content_length": 79, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776149777}, {"pid": 864549285, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 31, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 15:01", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864549027,45974302,3772]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38808210]纯生啤酒[/uid] (2026-04-14 15:00):[/b]<br/><br/>是最后机构们达成一致了吗，要去轮动的方向，所以尾盘猛猛操作。然后原来的方向先不猛出货，让看到指数涨的小散进来，然后明天砸了，最后逐步切到新的方向等散户抬轿[/quote]<br/>不用砸啊 为什么老是想要砸<br/>散户买就给他们就好了啊", "lou": 2043, "content_length": 51, "reply_to": 864549027, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776150115}, {"pid": 864550972, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 65, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 15:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "做好轮动就行 不要看太多方向  你们看不过来的 <br/>不要一个板块跳另一个板块  而是板块内轮动 逻辑已经说清楚了 。<br/>但是不要去弱智板块  比如白酒地产那些", "lou": 2044, "content_length": 130, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776150815}, {"pid": 864555073, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 23, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 15:40", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864554374,45974302,3778]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66907545]ptydd[/uid] (2026-04-14 15:35):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，特别想请教一个问题，看您是不是方便解惑，鹏辉在提示前就进的，但是有可能在您带领进的节点或者更早，就水灵灵的出来了。这种情况不止一两次了，想请教下，有没有可以学习改进的，谢谢狼大&amp;#128591;[img]./mon_202604/14/jmQ2x-46fmZbT3cSz0-m6.jpg[/img][/quote]<br/>你都没有持仓逻辑 卖飞就是正常的", "lou": 2045, "content_length": 35, "reply_to": 864554374, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776152412}, {"pid": 864556953, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 13, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 15:53", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864556559,45974302,3780]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65768926]好好看好好学不好[/uid] (2026-04-14 15:50):[/b]<br/><br/>，，其实一直有个疑问，所谓科技方向到底指的哪些板块呀，，ai硬包括光pcb电子布啥的，然后算力租赁，数据中心，电池机器人，这些不都是科技方向吗[s:ac:晕][/quote]<br/>高切低", "lou": 2046, "content_length": 11, "reply_to": 864556559, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776153210}, {"pid": 864558470, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 19, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 16:04", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864558045,45974302,3780]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67051352]九彩[/uid] (2026-04-14 16:01):[/b]<br/><br/>[size=120%]狼大，请问一下，为啥判断今天下午散户都在疯狂卖出啊？[/size][size=120%]<br/>我今天就盯着4000点那块反复摩擦，心里有点发怵，总觉得4000又要收过路费了。所以在大盘到4000的时候，忍不住先卖了三分之一的仓位。[/size][size=120%]<br/>没想到尾盘直接爆拉，心态有点崩[/size][/quote]<br/>散户是早上卖了  然后下午又被吸引回去了  看量能就懂了", "lou": 2047, "content_length": 53, "reply_to": 864558045, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776153844}, {"pid": 864561828, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 15, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 16:27", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864561511,45974302,3782]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61059514]lang丶[/uid] (2026-04-14 16:25):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，想请教下题材内部的高切低可不可行的？就像最近走的很好的光，前排已经冲新高的情况下，能不能去做一些低位补涨？毕竟现在还有一些票沿着五日线一直在走上升趋势的，但是涨幅没那么高的[/quote]<br/>光伏我不喜欢  目前走弱B反还有个强C  主要是前面没咋跌后面如果大盘走弱C他们可能走强C", "lou": 2048, "content_length": 83, "reply_to": 864561511, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776155237}, {"pid": 864568930, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 11, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 17:14", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864568112,45974302,3783]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61059514]lang丶[/uid] (2026-04-14 17:09):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，不是光伏而是光通信那些，例如一些光纤、光模块那些的部分低位走趋势的[s:ac:瞎]光伏我自己也不爱做[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>那些没问题  特别很多低位光都是二买位置准备就上来了", "lou": 2049, "content_length": 53, "reply_to": 864568112, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776158067}, {"pid": 864585493, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 75, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-14 19:46", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864422578,45974302,3703]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=150058]-阿狼-[/uid] (2026-04-13 14:49):[/b]<br/><br/>今天大概就这样了  还是那个预期  越靠近3950附近 越有机会 目标4030-4035  指数高度不多 但是补涨票还不错<br/>这段很好做 那种已经涨起来的板块的龙头不做 做他的二供<br/>暂时风险系数还行 至少指数能活到周3 按时间周期[/quote]<br/><br/>明天就是周三了 之后的时间注意了哦", "lou": 2050, "content_length": 37, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 864422578, "postdatetimestamp": 1776167209}, {"pid": 864624605, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 70, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-15 08:43", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[b]Reply to [pid=864624411,45974302,3793]Reply[/pid] Post by [uid=66989363]鱼饵啊啊[/uid] (2026-04-15 08:42)[/b]<br/>你为什么长脑子了？", "lou": 2051, "content_length": 49, "reply_to": 864624411, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776213828}, {"pid": 864634073, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 66, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-15 09:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "从现在开始  只关注一个事情，如果量能分时从放转缩超过15分钟，我开始转为谨慎。", "lou": 2052, "content_length": 74, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776218045}, {"pid": 864634929, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 38, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-15 09:59", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864634290,45974302,3803]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66989363]鱼饵啊啊[/uid] (2026-04-15 09:55):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大包括昨天机构切过来的低位板块吗？[s:ac:哭笑]&amp;#160;我替兄弟们问问。[/quote]<br/>低位就是拿来切换的  包括什么鬼  就是不想清仓的有点风偏的切过去<br/>我TM不是叫你们买药了么  这样都困不住你的钱？", "lou": 2053, "content_length": 105, "reply_to": 864634290, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776218367}, {"pid": 864643546, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 33, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-15 10:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "旅游家电起来了", "lou": 2054, "content_length": 14, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776221656}, {"pid": 864644339, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 21, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-15 10:59", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864644032,45974302,3817]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=1638060]三少爷的箭[/uid] (2026-04-15 10:57):[/b]<br/><br/>这是资金高低切，提前往低位的板块去避险吗，狼大。[/quote]<br/>这不是我昨天说的结论么<br/>现在出现了就是验证。", "lou": 2055, "content_length": 47, "reply_to": 864644032, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776221953}, {"pid": 864644394, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 8, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-15 10:59", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864644298,45974302,3817]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=36880300]13yu[/uid] (2026-04-15 10:58):[/b]<br/><br/>有个想法摸不准，分享出来跟大家讨论讨论。<br/>不知道有没有人关注到硫磺，作为硫酸原材料，已经从3000涨到6500了。现在国内供应fab的硫酸厂商都包不住成本要大幅涨价了(如晶瑞，兴福，江化微)。但涨价后，可能仅仅刚好够本。对财报来说营收增长，但利润降低很多，这算是利好还是利空。[/quote]<br/>利好  硫磺加工", "lou": 2056, "content_length": 17, "reply_to": 864644298, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776221971}, {"pid": 864645297, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 27, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-15 11:05", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864645009,45974302,3818]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=33490717]阿斯达斯d[/uid] (2026-04-15 11:03):[/b]<br/><br/>上午11点20左右如果放量砸到4012附近，感觉后面几天有希望如果谈判结果比较好的话有希望拉一波[/quote]<br/>跌破4034就已经不太好了  一旦市场更多的人发现了机构高切低 你说会不会形成短期踩踏", "lou": 2057, "content_length": 81, "reply_to": 864645009, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776222309}, {"pid": 864646072, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 29, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-15 11:09", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864645805,45974302,3819]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=37156751]伊泽瑞爾XD[/uid] (2026-04-15 11:08):[/b]<br/><br/>买点油对冲一下…[/quote]<br/>战争板块别看了<br/>上面有几个大哥套着散户  13块6的中石油里面的散户会压制整个板块。", "lou": 2058, "content_length": 80, "reply_to": 864645805, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776222591}, {"pid": 864646339, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 29, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-15 11:11", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864645964,45974302,3819]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=24264689]jscslinyu[/uid] (2026-04-15 11:09):[/b]<br/><br/>今天开盘冲高，高位科技就该跑了，可以减仓也可以切地位，认真爬楼的昨天就进来商航了 至少不会亏钱吧[/quote]<br/>商航还能亏钱？让他们出来给我看看哪个商航能亏钱的", "lou": 2059, "content_length": 53, "reply_to": 864645964, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776222685}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 36, "replies": 155490, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1782109329, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "c471167449", "digest": 0, "lastmodify": 1782109329, "tpid": 0, "post_misc_var": {"content_length": 412, "fid": 706, "comment_id": ",854270755,860174433", "14": {"17": 1, "14": 4, "13": 4, "12": 1}, "16": "63335896,19412700,26652007,67067074,20672033,66881586,67068843,66199622,60819388,60409766,67057614,60264977,61082281,42701832,66998841,61574956,61272875,67082978,66949654,65530601,60630412,60240136,66038632,63481990,61973100,60192597,66985104,19043499,39108806,41714633,7046671,65647302,40696141,3481707,654677,39235785,66063392,39314790,67071606,66251279,42126891,61602239,4785041,42995612,67024871,62241